<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM2.7.5">
<l>puḷḷiṉai vāypiḷan tiṭṭāy porukari yiṉkompo cittāy.</l>
<l>kaḷḷava rakkiyai mūkkoṭu kāvala ṉaittalai koṇṭā</l>
<l>yaḷḷinī veṇṇey viḻuṅka vañcā taṭiyē ṉaṭittēṉ</l>
<l>teḷḷiya nīri leḻunta ceṅkaḻu nīrcūṭṭa vārāy.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You who split the bird’s mouth!</l>
<l>You who snapped the war elephant’s tusk!</l>
<l>You who took the nose of the deceptive demoness</l>
<l rend="indent">and the head of [her] protector!</l>
<l>[And yet,] when you scooped up and devoured the butter,</l>
<l>I, your servant, beat you without fear.</l>
<l>Come, so that [I can] adorn [you] with the</l>
<l>red waterlily that grows in the clear water!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
